(2, '1685256874banner.jpg', '1685256874.jpg', NULL, NULL, '', 'Australia', 'Australia Study Visa Consultant In Pakistan', '<p>All the schools and <strong>allied institutions in Australia maintain well-structured</strong> curriculum that focuses on developing varied modern skills like critical &amp; analytical thinking, creativity, soft skills &amp; a communication, cultural exposure, leadership ability, ethical understanding and tons more. The Australian Government provides civil right for all international students to Study in Australia. The sole prerequisite is that one must obtain a Study visa for Australia.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"row align-items-center\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 pr-40 md-pr-15 md-mb-50\">\r\n<h2 class=\"mt-10 mb-0\">Key Information of Australian Study Visa</h2>\r\n<div class=\"sec-title4\">\r\n<div>The sort of visa you would like will depend upon your age, the course you would like to choose or got admission in, and the way long you\'d wish to stay in Australia. <br /><br />International students, mostly got to apply for a student visa &ndash; namely, subclass 500 regardless of their field of study. The subclass 500 came into existence on Dominion Day, 2016, which allows you to remain in Australia for the whole duration of your study. <br /><br />Usually, the courses won&rsquo;t last longer than five years. It\'s important for you to make sure that your Australia student visa remains valid, and you abide by the conditions as mentioned on your study visa. <br /><br />Australian visa for a student allows the aspirant to enter Australia up to 90 days before the course starts. Within seven days of arrival, the scholar must inform his/her education provider of the residential address, and also inform them within seven days if he/she changes the address in Australia. <br /><br /><strong>Student Visa validity:</strong> 1-2/3 years for all full-time courses.\r\n<h2 class=\"mt-10 mb-0\">Australia Study Visa Documents Requirements</h2>\r\n